    "updated_at": "2016-02-27T01:09:55Z",
    "body": "`openExternal` simply fires a URL at the OS and the OS decides which app to use to open it.  I don't think that it is possible to send headers/cookies with that URL.\n\nPerhaps you could implement an instant login feature inside your app that passes a token as a _GET_ parameter to the `openExternal` URL and logs them in to your website when that token is valid?\n"
